            "_type": "span",
            "_key": "e0fdf788-ea55-493c-96d9-c3cb586c5cc4",
            "text": "\n          <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<div data-mce-fragment=\"1\">\n<div data-selenium=\"overviewLongDescription\" class=\"\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\">\n<div class=\"js-injected-html\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\">\n<p data-mce-fragment=\"1\">The<span data-mce-fragment=\"1\">&nbsp;</span><b data-mce-fragment=\"1\">AudioQuest NRG-X2 US 2-prong Power Cable</b><span data-mce-fragment=\"1\">&nbsp;</span>is designed to reduce distortion in your signal chain. To achieve this the power cord utilizes long-grain copper in a helical array geometry with cold-weld connections. The long-grain copper has less oxides, less impurities, and less grain boundaries than industry standard oxygen-free high conductivity copper, which reduces the amount of interference within the cable. The geometry of the design influences the basic electrical properties of the cable, such as inductance and conductance. The use of cold-weld connections insures that the joints between the cable and hardware have a reduced influence influence on the signal clarity.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\">\n<div class=\"\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\">\n<div data-mce-fragment=\"1\">\n<div class=\"\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\">\n<h2 class=\"h2_2rws9renUitYEzmey3mjuE\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Cold-Weld System</h2>\n<div class=\"description_dROY_Wl-Y_I8SrM9_Ji7q\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\">\n<div class=\"js-injected-html\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Instead of traditional hot solder connections, the cables utilize a high pressure point of contact connection with copper or silver-impregnated paste, which maintains the structural integrity of the cable with a reduced influence on the signal clarity</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div data-mce-fragment=\"1\">\n<div class=\"\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\">\n<h2 class=\"h2_2rws9renUitYEzmey3mjuE\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Geometry</h2>\n<div class=\"description_dROY_Wl-Y_I8SrM9_Ji7q\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\">\n<div class=\"js-injected-html\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\">The cable utilizes a helical-array geometry, wherein the conductors spiral around one another which provides significantly better clarity and dynamic contrast than if the conductors are wrapped in multiple twisted pairs or run in parallel</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div data-mce-fragment=\"1\">\n<div class=\"\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\">\n<h2 class=\"h2_2rws9renUitYEzmey3mjuE\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Conductors</h2>\n<div class=\"description_dROY_Wl-Y_I8SrM9_Ji7q\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\">\n<div class=\"js-injected-html\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\">The power cable utilizes semi-solid concentric packed long-grain copper (LGC) conductors which reduce distortion by having larger strands that do not change position along the length of the cable and have fewer oxides, less grain boundaries, and less impurities than industry standard oxygen-free high conductivity copper</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n        "
