        "_key": "2c40cd7b-433b-4957-95f7-6bf72561404a",
        "title": "World-Class Noise Cancellation and Sound Shaped To You",
        "value": "The magic of CustomTune technology: it analyzes your ears and adapts the sound and active noise canceling to their unique shape. The result? World-class noise-cancelling earbuds and sound that's tailored to you.",
