        "title": "Listen Longer with Up To 24 Hours Total Play Time",
        "value": "QC Ultra Earbuds themselves give you up to 6 hours of listening time (up to 4   with Immersive Audio) while the included case holds up to three additional full charges. Pop the buds in the case for up to 2 hours of music from just a 20-minute charge.",
