        "_key": "7dc26cef-2d30-4522-a2ab-edcb64117455",
        "title": "Simple Touch-Free Device Controls",
        "value": "Wireless earbuds that give you full control. Play or pause music, change the volume, and switch tracks. You can even answer calls and change the noise cancellation level, all without ever touching your phone.",
