      },
      {
        "_type": "overviewField",
        "_key": "49058d62-9c09-414a-bd52-152de21e32b2",
        "title": "A Powerful Wireless Connection with Advanced Bluetooth 5.3",
        "value": "Bose Bluetooth earbuds offer a strong, continuous connection within 30 feet of your device. Choose single- or multi-point to keep your phone, tablet, and work or school computer paired or just focus on one.",
