        "information": "Features"
      },
      {
        "_type": "overviewField",
        "_key": "266b61c1-3772-48c4-bfa3-e1d6850d08ed",
        "title": "Triple Condenser Microphones For Perfect Streaming",
        "value": "Stream or record one, two, or more voices through three lightweight, fast-moving, and sensitive (37dB) 14mm condenser mics, cardioid, all with a wide, flat frequency range (50~16kHz). At 192kHz/24 bits recording, your streams and recordings will sound studioquality and capture every nuance of what you’re saying.",
        "information": "Product Feature"
      },
      {
        "_type": "overviewField",
        "_key": "3e60a39a-8733-417e-85b2-a06869c190bd",
        "title": "Four Selectable Voice Pick-Up Patterns",
        "value": "A single button on the microphone’s front quickly changes between four voice-pickup patterns: cardioid for when you’re recording or streaming by yourself, bi-directional if you’re interviewing someone on the opposite side of the mic, stereo if you and your co-host are sitting on the same side of the mic or you’re recording a musical instrument, and omnidirectional for any stream or podcast where more than two people are talking.",
        "information": "Product Feature"
      },
      {
        "_type": "overviewField",
        "_key": "28b36189-c838-4815-8966-6cee8f9d2251",
        "title": "Dynamic Range Compressor",
        "value": "Don’t worry about trying to talk at the same volume all the time: the dynamic range compressor keeps your voice from clipping if you get too loud, or gives you a boost if you’re speaking too softly.",
        "information": "Product Feature"
      },
      {
        "_type": "overviewField",
        "_key": "dd062756-6820-4c9c-8c85-897309295c16",
        "title": "Tap-To-Mute Button with RGB Ring Indicator",
        "value": "Feel a cough coming on? Just tap the touch sensor on top of the mic to mute yourself briefly. The RGB lights around the grille will turn red to remind you that your audience can’t hear you.",
        "information": "Product Feature"
      },
      {
        "_type": "overviewField",
        "_key": "02617223-e509-4e55-8625-f2682b4de76f",
        "title": "RGB VU Meter",
        "value": "Easily keep an eye on your volume levels with the real-time RGB VU meter that surrounds the control knob. Too low? Try turning up the gain. Going into the red? Your listeners might be hearing clipping and distortion, so ease back.",
        "information": "Product Feature"
      },
      {
        "_type": "overviewField",
        "_key": "e196e395-7a6c-4a4f-8920-7b7855538c4a",
        "title": "Easy Voice Monitoring",
        "value": "Monitor your voice directly from your headphones using the 3.5mm connection, controlling your volume on the microphone itself and using the included JBL QuantumENGINE software to adjust your EQ. You can also easily control the balance between PC sound and the amount of voice rerouted to your headset while streaming. The Audio/Voice Monitor feature allows for the best balance between the sound of your game and the level of your voice.",
        "information": "Product Feature"
      },
      {
        "_type": "overviewField",
        "_key": "98a89d44-1d6e-4049-a604-4802129ce940",
        "title": "Universal Mounting Solution",
        "value": "Use the included stand to hold the mic, or if you’ve already got a boom arm or C-clamp system in your setup, it will screw right into either.",
        "information": "Product Feature"
      },
      {
        "_type": "overviewField",
        "_key": "9a20ed2b-f504-4cea-87f2-cf446bd96032",
        "title": "Made from Premium and Sturdy Material",
        "value": "The JBL Quantum Stream Studio mic stands firm on the table thanks to the sturdy alloy stand made of zinc. Premium components such as the metal body and grill make this mic suitable for any professional streaming setup.",
        "information": "Product Feature"
      },
      {
        "_type": "overviewField",
        "_key": "d5534998-4bf3-4d4e-add7-7a8c3ba50fb4",
        "title": "JBL QuantumENGINE Compatibility",
        "value": "With the included JBL QuantumENGINE software, you can quickly adjust EQ and gain to fine-tune your sound, mute and unmute yourself, apply noise reduction, perform a quick mic test, and even customize the mic’s radiant RBG lighting, all from your computer screen.",
        "information": "Product Feature"
